title: 22. My Acne Journey: Treatments, Triggers + Straight Up Terrible Dates.
description:
Hi Roomies, in this episode, I want to talk about my journey with acne... I'm sharing:

The emotions I felt while dealing with acne.

How it made me a better + more powerful esthetician.

Tried and true acne methods.

Common triggers for acne.

And what NOT to do!
